{"noun":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/1a/9d/17517_crt_3RFZB.jpg?r=1433412239","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/1a/9d/17517_crt_3RFZB.jpg?r=1433412239","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/1a/9d/17517_crt_3RFZB.jpg?r=1433412239","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/1a/9d/17517_crt_3RFZB.jpg?r=1433412239"},"name":"アルスラーン","relation":"主角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/46/c8/3900_prsn_9Z9tZ.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/46/c8/3900_prsn_9Z9tZ.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/46/c8/3900_prsn_9Z9tZ.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/46/c8/3900_prsn_9Z9tZ.jpg"},"name":"山口勝平","short_summary":"日本の声優、劇団21世紀FOX所属舞台俳優、芸能プロダクション悟空代表。\r\n\r\n为人熟悉的代表配音作品有动画《乱马½》主角早乙女乱马〈男生〉、《犬夜叉》主角犬夜叉、《名侦探柯南》工藤新一、《魔术快斗》主角黑羽快斗／怪盗基德、《ONE PIECE》的骗人布、《死亡笔记本》的L、《我们这一家》的藤野等。\r\n兴趣和特长为画插图、弹吉他、杀阵。入读声优学校之前送过报纸。","career":["artist","seiyu"],"id":3900,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":17517},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/ef/e1/17519_crt_KAXyk.jpg?r=1433412290","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/ef/e1/17519_crt_KAXyk.jpg?r=1433412290","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/ef/e1/17519_crt_KAXyk.jpg?r=1433412290","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/ef/e1/17519_crt_KAXyk.jpg?r=1433412290"},"name":"ダリューン","relation":"主角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/59/f9/1582_prsn_N4nun.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/59/f9/1582_prsn_N4nun.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/59/f9/1582_prsn_N4nun.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/59/f9/1582_prsn_N4nun.jpg"},"name":"井上和彦","short_summary":"日本声优、解说、舞台演员、音响监督。神奈川县横滨市出身。B-Box所属。横浜市立横浜商業高等学校卒業。\r\n曾数度结婚、离婚。首任妻子为《小甜甜》的漫画家五十岚优美子(いがらしゆみこ)，之后又曾与声优荒川美奈子、女演员越智静香结婚，但最终均离婚。长子为漫画家兼女装模特五十岚奈波(いがらし奈波)，本名五十岚庆一(五十嵐慶一)。","career":["producer","artist","seiyu"],"id":1582,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":17519},{"images":{"small":"https://l